  "detailed_description": "Medianne Phirtia, a student residing in the region of Midgard. <br />\r\nShe has long held an admiration for 'Celestria' — a place spoken of in fairy tales where users of magic reside. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nDuring breaks from her studies, Medianne perused literature and documents about those fairy tales. It didn't take her long to determine that the fairy tales were more than stories! <br />\r\n<br />\r\nYes... The mysterious 'Phantasm Tower' in the very center of the world is the very entrance to Celestria!!",
